Package: earthtide
Type: Package
Title: R Parallel Implementation of Eterna 3.40 Predict and Analyze Code
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Jonathan", "Kennel", email = "jkennel@uoguelph.ca", role = c("aut", "cre", "trl")), 
             person("Beth", "Parker", email = "bparker@uoguelph.ca", role = c("ths")))
Maintainer: Jonathan Kennel <jkennel@uoguelph.ca>
Description: This is a port of Fortran Eterna 3.4 code <http://igets.u-strasbg.fr/soft_and_tool.php> for calculating synthetic earth tides. It has been rewritten in R and C++ for increased performance. 
